{"tid":1134972,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑呑左外賣筷子甩出黎嘅籤","createTime":"2019-05-02T04:33:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T04:52:46.000Z","uid":217479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f8b59461cdc63ed5a76aecffc504f4cc55991071","tid":1134972,"uid":217479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T04:33:31.000Z","msg":"話說我呢幾日一直喉嚨痛，睇左中醫同飲左感冒沖劑都冇咩點好過，越諗越覺得奇怪，其實我又冇任何感冒嘅病症<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又冇咳又冇聲沙，正正常常<br />\n但係就係一直feel到個喉嚨左邊好痛，有種好似俾嘢刮損嘅感覺，特別係食嘢嘅時候。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n諗諗下，記起好似前幾日外賣車仔麪，佢俾嘅嗰枝木筷子好似阿爺條撚咁，又梅又散，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />懷疑係嗰時呑左啲籖落肚，我依家可以點算。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"377aaee202d08ff6b3276ea3ab2130f9e90ed290","tid":1134972,"uid":132524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T04:36:06.000Z","msg":"可能刮傷左 <br />\n<br />\n或者去醫院照鏡"},{"pid":"9d2b35bc58b3e261f6f725ac91dc9ed60141b0cb","tid":1134972,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T04:38:57.000Z","msg":"遲d會拮穿你個喉嚨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c55a00b1c80fc87c4db1b84cb71f8b3c28b2750b","tid":1134972,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T04:45:35.000Z","msg":"你含過你呀爺條撚？"},{"pid":"113c1cd227504f0d0c4e41127b53345073d7031c","tid":1134972,"uid":217479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"377aaee202d08ff6b3276ea3ab2130f9e90ed290","tid":1134972,"uid":132524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T04:36:06.000Z","msg":"可能刮傷左 <br />\n<br />\n或者去醫院照鏡"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T04:50:53.000Z","msg":"診所會唔會都有得照<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e68a7d0ecaf9688362496d0156b0c6271d35457","tid":1134972,"uid":217479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c55a00b1c80fc87c4db1b84cb71